reviewText: Well done intro to the 787 and other Boeing airliners, including the lineup of all the "7" series polanes. Delivered very fast.
Can they just stick wit main idea?

This was the worst aviation documentary I have ever purchased. Don't buy it as it is a total ripoff. The video hardly even talks about the Boeing 787. Instead it shows planes taking off and landing at an airport which is not even worth watching.
This is truly a documentary.  Probably would not hold the interest of those not into airplane building.
